      "time_str": "00:46.700",
      "text": "风吹散落在天涯",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.18,
      "time_str": "00:50.180",
      "text": "爱不怕太傻 你的一句话",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 53.72,
      "time_str": "00:53.720",
      "text": "我用心牢牢记下",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.22,
      "time_str": "00:57.220",
      "text": "如果有一天你对我的爱只剩下残骸",
      "translation": null
    },
